classDiagram
    class Owner {
        +string name
        +int available_minutes
        +string preferences
        +update_preferences()
        +set_availability()
    }

    class Pet {
        +string name
        +string species
        +string care_notes
        +update_profile()
        +get_care_needs()
    }

    class Task {
        +string title
        +int duration_minutes
        +string priority
        +get_summary()
        +is_high_priority()
    }

    class Scheduler {
        +list tasks
        +Owner owner
        +Pet pet
        +generate_schedule()
        +sort_tasks()
        +filter_tasks()
        +explain_choice()
    }

    Owner "1" o-- "0..*" Pet : owns
    Scheduler --> Owner : uses
    Scheduler --> Pet : uses
    Scheduler --> Task : schedules